               <p>JOHN MATTHEY. I am a <rs id="t18170702-10-viclabel54" type="occupation">stockbroker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170702-10-victim137 t18170702-10-viclabel54"></join>. On the 8th of June, about ten o'clock at night, I was walking on <placeName id="t18170702-10-crimeloc55">Holborn-hill</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18170702-10-crimeloc55" type="placeName" value="Holborn-hill"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18170702-10-crimeloc55" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170702-10-off52 t18170702-10-crimeloc55"></join>, with a gentleman; the prisoner, in company with another man, was walking behind us - I turned round and saw the prisoner's hand come out of my pocket, with the handkerchief; I seized him, and accused him with taking it - He denied it, and at the same time threw it behind him - I saw him do it. I picked it up, and took him to the watch-house.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I did not take it.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18170702-10-verdict56" type="verdictDescription">
